---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Cpu, MapPin, UtensilsCrossed } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Jonathan Diaz" sideBarActiveItemID="about">
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">About Me</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-base-content/80">
      Engineer, builder, and curiosity-driven problem solver.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <Cpu class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
        Engineering
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/90">
        I enjoy building technical systems that combine math, software, and real-world sensing. 
        I'm drawn to problems where estimation, filtering, and computer vision meet practical deployment—tracking systems, 
        sensor fusion pipelines, and AI-assisted tools that work in real conditions.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base-content/90 mt-4">
        I like turning theory into working systems: Kalman filters that run on embedded hardware, 
        vision pipelines that handle messy real-world data, and algorithms that bridge research and production.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <MapPin class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
        Florida Springs
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/90">
        Outside of engineering, I love exploring Florida's natural springs. We've been to Wekiva, Silver, Blue, De Leon, 
        and several others around central Florida. There's something special about swimming in crystal-clear water 
        and seeing the underwater world—it never gets old.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <UtensilsCrossed class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
        Food
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/90">
        I enjoy eating all kinds of foods, from KBBQ to seafood boils and everything in between. 
        Always down to try something new.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-base-200 border border-base-300">
      <p class="text-base-content/90 italic">
        "I enjoy building technical systems that combine math, software, and real-world sensing. 
        Outside of engineering I enjoy exploring Florida's springs, experimenting with new projects, 
        and continuously learning."
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
